OL,3,CDismembered pensioner called alleged
OL,4,Ckiller his 'partner', jury hears
OL,6,FA pensioner murdered and sawn into 27
OL,7,Fpieces told an online friend he was
OL,8,Fthe partner of the man now accused of
OL,9,Fkilling him, a court heard.
OL,11,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, denies
OL,12,Fmurdering and dismembering Stuart
OL,13,FEverett, 67, whose body parts he
OL,14,Fallegedly deposited at various sites
OL,15,Facross Salford and Manchester.
OL,17,FMr Everett sent emails to the friend
OL,18,Fcalling his alleged killer by the name
OL,19,Fof "Kamil" and describing him as his
OL,20,F"partner", a jury at Manchester Crown
OL,21,FCourt heard.
