OL,3,CDismembered pensioner called alleged
OL,4,Ckiller his 'partner', jury hears
OL,6,FA murder investigation was launched
OL,7,Ffollowing the discovery of Mr
OL,8,FEverett's torso in Kersal Dale nature
OL,9,Freserve, Salford, on 4 April 2024.
OL,11,FMr Everett, originally from Derby and
OL,12,Fborn Roman Ziemacki from Polish
OL,13,Fparents, and Majerkiewicz, from
OL,14,FPoland, lived together with another
OL,15,FPolish man in Winton, Salford.
OL,17,FIt is alleged Majerkiewicz killed Mr
OL,18,FEverett through severe blows to his
OL,19,Fhead overnight between 27-28 March
OL,20,F2024 at the house they shared.
