OL,3,CDismembered pensioner called alleged
OL,4,Ckiller his 'partner', jury hears
OL,6,FHe is then alleged to have then
OL,7,Fdismembered the pensioner with a
OL,8,Fhacksaw and taken numerous bus trips
OL,9,Fcarrying body parts in bags on
OL,10,F"deposition journeys" to get rid of
OL,11,Fthe evidence.
OL,13,FJurors were told only around one third
OL,14,Fof Mr Everett's body has been
OL,15,Frecovered.
OL,17,FBen Campbell, prosecution junior, told
OL,18,Fthe jury of agreed facts, not disputed
OL,19,Fby defence lawyers for Majerkiewicz.
