OL,3,CDismembered pensioner called alleged
OL,4,Ckiller his 'partner', jury hears
OL,6,FMr Campbell said Stuart Everett met a
OL,7,Fwoman called Yvonne Hank online
OL,8,Fthrough YouTube in 2021 and began
OL,9,Fexchanging emails.
OL,11,F"Within the emails Stuart Everett
OL,12,Findicated that his partner was called
OL,13,FKamil, with a 'K'."
OL,15,FMr Campbell said in one email
OL,16,Fexchange, Stuart Everett provided a
OL,17,Fphoto of Kamil.
