OL,6,F"The photo was of Marcin
OL,7,FMajerkiewicz," Mr Campbell added. He
OL,8,Falso told Ms Hank that Kamil's
OL,9,Fbirthday was 10 April ` the same
OL,10,Fbirthday date as Majerkiewicz.
OL,12,FIn March 2021, she replied to an email
